test_even_range:
assert [7] == [4, 6, 8, 10, 12]
  At index 0 diff: 7 != 4
  Right contains 4 more items, first extra item: 6
  Full diff:
  - [4, 6, 8, 10, 12]
  + [7]
test_large_range:
assert [1005] == [2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
  At index 0 diff: 1005 != 2
  Right contains 4 more items, first extra item: 3
  Full diff:
  - [2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
  + [1005]
